{"tid":1026422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蝻亞撞車黨　蹺腳瞓地兼開聲要錢","createTime":"2019-02-18T06:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T08:24:54.000Z","uid":225464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"69f35bfad8a3e7da666fab7c5a06cbfd241cf0c0","tid":1026422,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:08:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>南亞漢疑化身撞車黨 蹺腳瞓地兼開聲要錢</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2V2CAuT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2V2CAuT&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=c34f7390\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2V2CAuT</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190218/photo/bkn-20190218134858640-0218_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190218140131\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190218134858640-0218_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190218140131&h=3b97b49a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暈完醒番玩電話？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又有撞車黨出沒？近日元朗有南亞漢疑佯裝被車撞倒，瞓在地上後竟朝司機嚷︰「Money Money」？<br />\n<br />\n網民Lwn Roman和Lau Sai Wah在Facebook專頁「盡在元朗」分享事件，指周一（18日）早上約8時半，元朗壽富街與福康街交界，有南亞漢突然從行人路步出，躺在一輛正轉彎的私家車前。<br />\n<br />\n從照片可見，該南亞漢閉着眼睛，高舉雙手呈大字形躺在馬路。另一張相片則見，他蹺着腳躺在車前，意識清醒地撳着電話。目擊者指︰「睇住佢自己瞓低，仲大聲講Money Money」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民怒斥：「無賴」、「碰瓷國際化」、「交戲交足全套啦，啲戲咁屎，點畀錢呀」，又嘆言：「依家少個車Cam都唔掂」。"},{"pid":"e63e71f3e75597e1f66303d35117fb309659d1c6","tid":1026422,"uid":60796,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:37:39.000Z","msg":"同蝗一鳩樣"},{"pid":"6939d16487c7d8f3a34a3aee96ca28d2595f2275","tid":1026422,"uid":205844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:40:52.000Z","msg":"moneymoney<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212370b9040efacc80ea596c0d2ad71cab3ec9f0","tid":1026422,"uid":619,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"ci